Package edu.salleurl.profile

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Profileable
    This interface stablishes the minimum getters a class should implement for it to represent an entity that can have an associated profile.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Profile
    Class able to generate an HTML profile of any class implementing the Profileable interface, alongside some extra data.
    ProfileFactory
    Factory class for generating instances of the Profile class.
